- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is the most likely category as the paper deals with regular equations and their solutions, which are fundamental concepts in this field. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is also likely as the paper discusses a computational interpretation of solving regular equations. 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is relevant as regular expressions and equations are often used in formal logic. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) could be a possible category as the paper discusses algorithms for solving regular equations. 
- cs.SC (Symbolic Computation) is also a possible category as the paper deals with algebraic methods for solving regular equations.
